::DrillBit::

The one ion disk hit him in the side, as he destroyed the other with a
optic blast. After regaining his balance, he shot two optics at Depth
Charge's face, and several rounds from his gattaling gun.

::Epyon::

"Ah, Wizard. We are going to merge the Cybertronian Fire, StarJumper,
and another Maximal ship to form a Maximal City. We need to prepare the
ship for deconstruction. And as soon as myself and Prowl agree to go
ahead with it, we'll start."
He looked very pleased.
"This will give us the edge in this war."

::Hot Rod::

He got out of the CR chamber, and made his way to the mess hall.
He sat down, and had a glass of energon.

::Demolition::

He saw the Cybertronian Fire come into view.
"There it is Havoc!"

::Dollon::

There was still no responce from the traders.
"Oh this is cute! Set up the deal and then not show!"
